eventDecorators.name: Paused
eventDecorators.description: Notifies when found an error decoding request result. Emitted when the pause is triggered by `account`.

eventDecorators.name: Unpaused
eventDecorators.description: Notifies when found an error decoding request result. Emitted when the pause is lifted by `account`.

functionDecorators.name: pause
functionDecorators.description: Triggers stopped state. Requirements: - The contract must not be paused.

functionDecorators.name: unpause
functionDecorators.description: Returns to normal state. Requirements: - The contract must be paused.
